OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FStaying dry and cloudy or
OL,6,Fbright with some mist possible during
OL,7,Fthe morning. Occasional sunny spells
OL,8,Fdeveloping and winds light, turning
OL,9,Finto the north or northwest.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FDry but probably rather
OL,12,Fcloudy, the best of any breaks in the
OL,13,Fevening with some sunny spells
OL,14,Fpossible. Winds light or moderate from
OL,15,Fthe north.
OL,16,
OL,17,CFriday:FStaying dry and cloudy or
OL,18,Fbright with the cloud expected to thin
OL,19,Fand break at times. Feeling cool and
OL,20,Ffresh at times with light to moderate
OL,21,Fnorth or northwest.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
